# Git Constraints

Never commit generated pipeline artifacts to version control. This includes but is not limited to:
- `.wav` audio files
- `.json` timestamps or other generated JSON payloads (unless explicitly intended as a static test fixture)
- `.mp4` video files
- The entire contents of the `data/workspace/` directory or its subdirectories.